{"tid":1813797,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大宿生購大量N95口罩　憂內地生染病後校內傳播","createTime":"2020-01-06T13:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T14:07:52.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1859007e62d2bbed49402fa4c350fc84195ec07d","tid":1813797,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"內地武漢爆發不明原因肺炎疫情，香港中文大學有女生亦曾到武漢、之後又出現發燒、呼吸道感染或肺炎症狀的病例。一名20歲女學生由武漢回港後出現發燒及有上呼吸道感染症狀，前往仁安醫院求診被拒，最終被送往公立醫院。據悉她居於聯合書院伯利衡宿舍 (伯宿)，宿生人心惶惶，擔心疫情爆發，紛紛戴口罩防疫，有學生購買多個N95口罩。有宿生指，由於伯宿及毗鄰宿舍有不少內地生居住，擔心他們返回內地後受到感染，並在校內傳播，故過去數天，學生、工友等均已戴上口罩。有內地生稱不擔心會爆發肺炎，認為校方會做好清潔消毒工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808771/org/8710be927cab034477150de34f76e40f.jpg/pW8cCBud0j88S0bp84ku8fRJtMM4Y8jWic1_saPNf7E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808771%2Forg%2F8710be927cab034477150de34f76e40f.jpg%2FpW8cCBud0j88S0bp84ku8fRJtMM4Y8jWic1_saPNf7E&h=44a70398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓李男學生及姓鄭女學生指過去數天已一直戴口罩。（林振華攝）<br />\n<br />\n姓李男學生及姓鄭女學生戴口罩到伯利衡宿舍了解情況，他們指過去數天得知香港有懷疑個案後，便開始戴口罩，而且伯利衡宿舍有較多內地學生，擔心他們會受到感染，故大家戴口罩保護自己。伯利衡宿舍及毗連宿舍的宿生、工友皆已戴上口罩，「都擔心，比較多內地生，比較難追蹤佢哋有冇去武漢。」他們指未接獲校方提醒要加強防疫意識。<br />\n<br />\n另一名葉同學表示，得知宿舍有一名女學生曾往武漢後發燒，其後有醫院方面的人士到宿舍，而女學生被送往醫院。他擔心有疫情爆發，故已經準備大量N95口罩，惟未見校方進行消毒清潔。他指與女宿生分住不同樓層，暫未計劃進行清潔。<br />\n<br />\n居住在伯宿的林同學指，因為明天是學期開始，故要回宿舍作準備。他表示，懷疑發燒的女學生居於五樓，學生群組指有穿保護衣人士到五樓清潔。由於宿舍有不少內地生居住，故擔心會有同學在內地染病，在宿舍內傳播。他指只能戴口罩預防。<br />\n<br />\n來自上海的陳同學表示，認為校方會做好消毒，不擔心肺炎爆發，自己也會加緊清潔，「我覺得哪怕真的有（有人染病），不是不正常的事情，因為可能確實有同學從武漢過來不小心感染肺炎。」但他相信學校會進行清潔消毒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808778/org/e26cb1f9000ac49c4d8e83abc2cee674.jpg/nAEUqZugOOu4PbxWq6X_jcnY0q1NkWTYKOsc7yjrHO8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808778%2Forg%2Fe26cb1f9000ac49c4d8e83abc2cee674.jpg%2FnAEUqZugOOu4PbxWq6X_jcnY0q1NkWTYKOsc7yjrHO8&h=3e2cb1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808780/org/d715ff7b31bee0970193c7607ce4e967.jpg/cKDQ4hvjpxDYDMNi7q2lf_QHI-m8YIJD1utBetbrQXo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808780%2Forg%2Fd715ff7b31bee0970193c7607ce4e967.jpg%2FcKDQ4hvjpxDYDMNi7q2lf_QHI-m8YIJD1utBetbrQXo&h=4d1bb592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808779/org/47970ea87688310bc615d5e2e7f8e905.jpg/ZY_jr_8VxKEmhhVXMix-_aiVbjnKLGsiP8wQZz_MEGc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808779%2Forg%2F47970ea87688310bc615d5e2e7f8e905.jpg%2FZY_jr_8VxKEmhhVXMix-_aiVbjnKLGsiP8wQZz_MEGc&h=ac9abc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808782/org/7f38a89835a606209840b82ad50e1ec6.jpg/RenxLkr6RFHDW0acPAkaStuDZd841l-Vc-mu-3Pprvs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808782%2Forg%2F7f38a89835a606209840b82ad50e1ec6.jpg%2FRenxLkr6RFHDW0acPAkaStuDZd841l-Vc-mu-3Pprvs&h=88fac581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808781/org/663e53343ced9f711b7789a7497a5631.jpg/dU_Fi-Ys3Mut1sp472G-5msZJGGNfzISoMt_4KDLf-A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808781%2Forg%2F663e53343ced9f711b7789a7497a5631.jpg%2FdU_Fi-Ys3Mut1sp472G-5msZJGGNfzISoMt_4KDLf-A&h=3eaa4693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808837/org/e8702409979111d12e65565a854b48e7.JPG/0uFuKR5BmeOPM2oXHtYm4XnQEtjgj7dXISphsiEqYbI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808837%2Forg%2Fe8702409979111d12e65565a854b48e7.JPG%2F0uFuKR5BmeOPM2oXHtYm4XnQEtjgj7dXISphsiEqYbI&h=9f30e054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808836/org/745c7dae1a4b4beb8fd3ec9e81e3052a.jpg/4W9me-iJogNr8YDvQBaGdwp-G-ZY2dWIbQ8O820PDvM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808836%2Forg%2F745c7dae1a4b4beb8fd3ec9e81e3052a.jpg%2F4W9me-iJogNr8YDvQBaGdwp-G-ZY2dWIbQ8O820PDvM&h=535cf25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港中文大學回應事件表示，中大有一名學生離港後於12月29日返港，於1月4日感到身體不適，今天（5日）早上返宿舍後，曾外出往私家醫院求診，及後自行前往深圳的醫院跟進檢查。該同學傍晚回到宿舍，在救護人員陪同下，她和其同房宿生一同前往公立醫院作進一步檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n中大表示，大學隨即按照衛生防護中心的指引，以漂白水清潔該學生的房間、居住樓層及公眾地方，以保障宿生健康，亦將衞生防護中心的健康指引張貼在宿舍告示板供同學參考。該宿舍並會提供手術口罩、酒精搓手液給宿生使用。若同學感到不適或有顧慮，可前往大學保健處進行檢查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3808783/org/a3192c057838e9a421cb509090027d2c.jpg/FcTZAmwkrtLN4OqXrXi_Z_1J1oEgN7K9ZlIiQWZSIkE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3808783%2Forg%2Fa3192c057838e9a421cb509090027d2c.jpg%2FFcTZAmwkrtLN4OqXrXi_Z_1J1oEgN7K9ZlIiQWZSIkE&h=694d23d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前曾有穿保護衣人士出入伯宿。（CUHK Secrets圖片）<br />\n<br />\n撰文：楊婉婷林振華<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/417971/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%BF%E7%94%9F%E8%B3%BC%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8Fn95%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%86%82%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%9F%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E5%BE%8C%E6%A0%A1%E5%85%A7%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F417971%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258Fn95%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%2586%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2592%25AD&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDezsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=29341979\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/417971/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%BF%E7%94%9F%E8%B3%BC%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8Fn95%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%86%82%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%9F%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85%E5%BE%8C%E6%A0%A1%E5%85%A7%E5%82%B3%E6%92%AD</a>"},{"pid":"5bfa16163f9d67de3bc730fff37e0a750321f896","tid":1813797,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}